storyInfo: Catapult, wanted for blowing up a noble lord's private vault, escapes from her hometown with help.

attributes.content: Don't move. Hide fast. They're here.
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Head inside. In. Right, don't make a peep!
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Alright, alright, sir, don't break your bones knocking.
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Thanks for keeping us safe. Is everything okay?
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Orders from Lord Barth! Searching for a suspect!
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: (Bro, Filon, what's the deal? What's the 'sir' for...)
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: (Gotta put up the act in front of other people, right, Sir Raz?)
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Searching for a suspect?! Absolutely, search by all means!
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: But I can tell you there's no suspects in here, sir! We're all good people, I want you to see that!
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: (Pffheehee.)
(The cupboard makes a rocking sound.)
What was that noise?
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: Is there anyone else in your house?
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: N—No. Do you see anyone else? I don't...
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Maybe you heard wrong, sir?
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Did I? But...
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: Fine. Look at the size of this place. We'd know if someone was here.
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: And I didn't hear anything. You're on edge.
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Alright... if you say so.
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: Sirs, are you here for...
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: This has nothing to do with you. We're done here.
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Remember to immediately report any tips to the search team!
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Yeah, I will, I will.
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Yeesh, are they finally gone?
Hey, stay in there!
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Keep it down, they're still close...
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: It's cool, it's cool, Filon, bro. C'mon, unclench those cheeks.
Raz must've heard me a moment ago, didn't he? I mean, he held it in, and he's not gonna turn back to bust me now.
Relax, relax.
I mean, he probably wants to let you go, but the guys behind him might be a different story.
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: You're the only woman I've ever met who'd straight-up bomb some old noble's vault, not to mention the part where you drove out throwing the guy's treasure all over the place...
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Seriously, Catapult, can you guess how much you're worth right now?
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Haha, I bet it can't be as much as all that treasure I left you~
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Heh, you got me there.
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Honestly, though, where do you get the guts to do this stuff?
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: That was all his best stuff in that safe, y'know! Hah, he's lost his mind. If he catches you for real, he'll be mad enough to peel you like a yucca!
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Fly in, go boom, fly out. I've gotta do this nickname you all give me a little justice, right?
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: You can only take so much before your back breaks, you know? I'm at my limit with that old-ass... It's not about guts. I was practically forced to do that.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: I'm good now, see. I'm refreshed, and everyone gets a little something nice out of it. Peace and love for all, right?
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Forced, my ass. Some people wouldn't hit back if their lives depended on it.
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: *sigh*. I'm gonna be honest, Arleta.
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Whoa, why so formal? Just gonna wave my real name like that, huh.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: I'm being real with you. I still think... there's nothing in this for you.
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Like, what does it get you? 'cause your gold, jewelry, bills... you haven't held onto a single thing, you threw it all over town.
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: What's your plan?
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: What's in for me? Heh, c'mon... does everything I do need some kinda paycheck?
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: ...*sigh*. That's not what I mean.
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: I just—look. You're the old geezer's private army, and he has your share of the pot to give. The tax levy doesn't even come round to you, and if you wanted, you could top up by skimming off all the dues.
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: When have I ever pocketed your money?
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: You haven't! If you did, you wouldn't be the first, and I would've shoved you out there.
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: That's what I'm getting at, at any rate. You live an alright life. You're a far cry from all of us, when we've got days we pay the tax and can't eat afterwards...
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: What are you actually thinking, Arleta?
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: If I just said I was done with that old fart, no other ideas going on, would you believe me?
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: No.
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Didn't think so.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Okay then, I need a minute. Lemme come up with some reason for you, ha.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Hey... I'm trying to be as straight as possible here. I don't know, can't you be a little serious?
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Bleeugh—you know me, Filon. It's the way I am.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Fine. No more jokes.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: I should be outta here soon, anyway. No good sticking around yours forever. Can't let this spiral out, or they'll make hell for you too.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: If I jump now, maybe I can rustle my way into a merchant caravan heading out of town.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Did you plan this out beforehand?
attributes.name: Townsfolk

attributes.content: Yeah, I don't actually wanna get flayed by the old guy either.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: See you later, then...
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Pass it on to all the people, if anyone else decides to squeeze their lives out, another explosion as coincidental as that vault might just be on the table.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Never, ever, ever sit there and wait for death like that again.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (This van's a cramped fit... I can't stretch my legs straight.)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (What's this thing even carrying? It's got a smell, alright... good thing I don't get carsick.)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (Ups to my luck, though. Two checkpoints down easy.)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (Good thing I already scoped how the caravan likes to go. It's the perfect ride to hitch.)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (As long as this holds, we just need to cross that bridge, and I should be on my way outta this dump.)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (Once I'm clear, then next, I'll head to... to...)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (Where? Shoot, I have no idea.)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (*yawn* I'm a little sleepy...)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: ...over there... ...nothing...
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: ...still haven't found them?
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: (Huh? Why is the search team out here?!)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (He really doesn't wanna give up the chase, huh? C'mon, guy, you're being way too clingy!)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (Let's take a look...)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Sirs, what—what are you looking for?
attributes.name: Hurrying Worker

attributes.content: We're searching for a suspect. Cooperate with us, please.
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Raz, we've checked over there! We found nothing suspicious!
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: Alright, you can pass now.
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Ugh, finally, on our way.
attributes.name: Hurrying Worker

attributes.content: Phew, I'm wiped. Do we have to keep on searching each one like this?
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: That's the old man's orders.
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: But how much longer do we have to search? We've been going door to door without a break since morning, and now we have to head out all this way.
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: If it wasn't for the bounty, I would've given up a while ago.
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: Weren't you clapping and cheering when you heard someone blew the man's vault out?
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Of course I was!
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: It was his private hoard, and now it's in the hands of all the poor common folk! I mean, mwah, who wouldn't give a story like that a thumbs up? Too perfect even for a Columbian movie!
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: So you...
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: That's that, this is this. None of the money made it into my hands.
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: Besides, who'd be on hard times with that reward? The miser's being generous for once!
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: (Haha! Looks like I really do have a good price tag.)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (No chance of getting over now, seeing how this all panned out. Even if I hide in a box, they could find me sooner or later...)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (Gotta do it. Times like these, your only choice is—)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (Hup!)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Ergh! My ass!
attributes.name: Hurrying Worker

attributes.content: Oof, I'm not hurt... no, wait, where's my wallet? Did someone just steal my wallet?!
attributes.name: Hurrying Worker

attributes.content: Thief... there's a thief! Catch the thief!
attributes.name: Hurrying Worker

attributes.content: Quit the racket! What happened?
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Knight, sir...! Th—Th—There's a thief!
attributes.name: Hurrying Worker

attributes.content: (And one more for the road...!)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (Check me out!)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Waagh! Wh—What the hell?
attributes.name: Passing Merchant

attributes.content: Yeek! Sir Knight, some bastard just felt me... Hey, you were right there! Was it you?!
attributes.name: Passing Traveler

attributes.content: Eh? I didn't do it... hey, what are you hitting me for?! Seriously, it wasn't me!
attributes.name: Innocent Passerby

attributes.content: Settle down, please, settle down!
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: All of you, calm down... don't get hysterical!
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Where's my wallet?!
attributes.name: Hurrying Worker

attributes.content: Back up, everyone! Our search here isn't over yet... ugh!
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: Who threw that stone?!
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: I can't take it anymore! Tell me, how much longer am I going to be stuck here?
attributes.name: Passing Traveler

attributes.content: I've gotten official passage! I request to be let through here immediately!
attributes.name: Passing Traveler

attributes.content: Hold on, this is by Lord Barth's command—
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: He's just a cruddy knight noble with a hunk of land. Who does he think he is?
attributes.name: Innocent Passerby

attributes.content: (Hahaha!)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (Mm-hm, and there's my moment.)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Phew...
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Finally, out of there.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Apologies, Mister, I'll toss your wallet in your van. And you over there, Miss, truly very sorry, I'll let you sock me sometime...
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: But sorry's all I can give right now!
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: See ya, everybody~
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: You're better off apologizing to their faces than doing it out here to the trees.
Stir chaos, hide in the crowd and slip out of the mess. You almost fooled me.
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Oh, hey, it's you.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Still got caught, huh? That's not good.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: I would've gotten away with it too, if it weren't for your sharp eyes, Raz.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Speaking of, when'd you put all this gear on? You look pretty slick, really like a capital-K Knight. May as well enroll for knighthood sometime, right?
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: The old fart's always been wanting to raise up a Knightclub.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: This road... should take me to my destination, if I'm not mistaken.
Hm?
Oh? What's that up there...?
Nothing else to say?
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Have a care, huh? I'm gonna look real long-winded if it's just me talking, y'know~
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: What, you're not here to cuff me and take me back? If you don't do anything, I'm gonna get away, alright? I'm warning you.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: If I was going to bring you in, I would've busted you back at Filon's.
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: If I actually did that... chances are Lord Barth would give you a public hanging for real.
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: True that, hahaha. Old guy's gotta be blowing his top!
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: So why'd you chase me out here anyway? Did you wanna give me a ride?
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Yes...
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: ...Whuh?
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Raz. Raz, bro.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Any way you slice it, the old guy's got all hands out for me. I'm wanted by name... You're deserting, here!
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: And you get to talk?
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Who slinked off to hit up the streets and go drinking, back when we were on patrol together—
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Stoppit, stoppit, let's not reopen old wounds. Bad.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: I came to ask you, why—
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Why let go of the good days, and risk it all on this?
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: ...Yeah.
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Man, it's not healthy to be stale like this~ Why's everyone ask this one question?
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: And if I confess it was just 'cause I was sick of the old guy, you don't even believe me!
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: I believe you.
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Guh?
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: It's a majorly convincing reason, knowing you.
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Are you commending me, or dunking on me... Filon sure didn't believe me one bit.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Whatever. We're way past that, now. Let me be real with you.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Under the geezer, as long as we do what we're told, we get everything taken care of, and we get a little allowance. And sure, maybe a whole lot consider those fine days to live.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: But I just couldn't stand it anymore. Everything that happens everywhere pisses you off. That life grosses me out, down to the core.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: But I can't say that in front of the people in that town. I can't drop those words.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: I've never gone hungry. How do I have the right to tell people without a meal to eat that I think my life sucks?
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: So you did it for all the civvies who couldn't pay taxes...
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Yeuch, don't make me out like some kind of beacon of righteousness. I'm not THAT good-hearted.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: I wasn't counting on doing something for anyone else's sakes. Blowing that geezer's vault open, dumping everything in there everywhere, that was all just me channeling my revenge.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Simple as that~
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Oh, my...
She's a surprisingly clear-minded girl.
But still, not quite that cautious...
Raz—!
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: What are you doing here?
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: Oh, crap, they're coming this way! Hide somewhere, quick!
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Easy for you to say... there's nowhere to hide here, is there?!
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Raz? What are you doing... are you talking to somebody?
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: I—
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: (Crap, I can't make it!)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Excuse me, sorry for that. I was occupying this kind gentleman's time.
(—Who?)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (She walked out from behind... was she seriously behind me the whole time?!)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Hm? Who is it?
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: You're... wait, it can't be, i—it's you?!
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: Pardon me. Please, don't be so nervous. I'm just a traveler passing through.
I was asking this gentleman the way just now.
Huh... is that right?
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: Uh... yeah, that's right.
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Um, forgive me, but are you... by any chance, the Candle Knight?
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Ah. That is indeed my title.
The Candle Knight?! THE renowned Knight from Leithanien... I've seen a whole bunch of your matches!
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: I never expected to meet someone as famous as you here! C... Could you, um, sign—sign this for me, Miss Knight?
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: I appreciate your praise. If just my signature suffices, I would be delighted.
(This lady's totally distracting everyone!)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (Just who...)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (Shh.)
(Is she winking at me...?!)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: This doesn't seem too well a place for conversation. If you don't mind, shall we talk as we go?
I've been wanting to pay a visit to the good Lord of this place, as it turns out... so could I trouble you all to show me the way?
Of course... of course!
attributes.name: Search Team Member

attributes.content: (She led them off for real... Did she—save me?)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (Catapult.)
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: (What?)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (To be honest, I didn't have any other real reason to come find you.)
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: (I just wanted to tell you this, personally... I don't have your courage, but I admire you.)
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: (This little town's too little. Maybe this whole place confines you, in a way.)
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: (Seize the moment. Go on.)
attributes.name: Patrolling Knight

attributes.content: Ahh...
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: What a nightmare. Here I was banking on having all my bills settled, and I could start my new life free as the wind.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: If I think about it, I've racked up new favors along the way now.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Nyeaah...
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Oh, well~ I've got a few decent bros in my old haunt I can think back on, and that's not a bad feeling~
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: And that Candle Knight lady. What a serious weirdo... but she helped me out big time, so consider my 100% fan loyalty as my payment!
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: I guess this really is goodbye... everyone.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: See you again...
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Phew...
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Alright, time to really think about it now. Where should I be off to next, I wonder~
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Hm...
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Well, let's leave Kazimierz for starters, and go see what the world beyond is like!
attributes.name: Catapult
